    - Now: import jakarta.validation.Valid;
  - src/main/java/com/java_template/application/controller/ProjectController.java
    - Replaced: import javax.validation.Valid;
    - Now: import jakarta.validation.Valid;

  Reason: With Jakarta EE / Spring Boot 3 on Java 21, the validation API lives under jakarta.validation, not javax.validation.

- Added missing import for CompletableFuture:
  - src/main/java/com/java_template/application/processor/ProjectEnterInProgressProcessor.java
    - Added: import java.util.concurrent.CompletableFuture;

  Reason: Code used CompletableFuture but the class import was missing, causing "cannot find symbol" compile errors.

